title: Plat ADC LF Duo or Team
body:
I'm plat 5 looking for either a support duo que, or a team. Preferably someone who's at least gold 1. 
My main adc's are Corki, Cait and Lucian. I'm learning Kalista and Draven next.
Just add me in game and and see where we go from there I guess.
